---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';

const whatsappUrl = 'https://wa.me/5491122611627?text=Hola%2C%20quiero%20diagnosticar%20mi%20cultivo';
---

<Layout title="Zea — Diagnostico Inteligente de Cultivos">
  <nav>
    <div class="logo">
      <div class="logo-icon">Z</div>
      Zea
    </div>
    <ul class="nav-links">
      <li><a href="#how">Como funciona</a></li>
    </ul>
    <a href={whatsappUrl} class="nav-cta" target="_blank">Diagnosticar cultivo</a>
  </nav>

  <section class="hero">
    <div class="hero-badge">
      <span class="dot"></span>
      Aleph Hackathon 2026
    </div>
    <h1>
      Diagnostico de cultivos<br />
      con <span class="highlight">peptidos antimicrobianos</span>
    </h1>
    <p class="hero-sub">
      Envia una foto de tu cultivo por WhatsApp. Nuestro agente identifica el patogeno
      y recomienda peptidos antimicrobianos personalizados — ciencia de laboratorio
      directo al campo.
    </p>
    <div class="hero-actions">
      <a href={whatsappUrl} class="btn-primary" target="_blank">Probar por WhatsApp</a>
      <button class="btn-secondary" onclick="document.getElementById('how').scrollIntoView({behavior:'smooth'})">
        Como funciona
      </button>
    </div>

    <div class="stats">
      <div class="stat">
        <div class="stat-value">$3.1B</div>
        <div class="stat-label">Agroquimicos AR / anio</div>
      </div>
      <div class="stat">
        <div class="stat-value">20-40%</div>
        <div class="stat-label">Perdida de cosechas</div>
      </div>
      <div class="stat">
        <div class="stat-value">800</div>
        <div class="stat-label">Cooperativas registradas</div>
      </div>
      <div class="stat">
        <div class="stat-value">112K</div>
        <div class="stat-label">Productores asociados</div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section" id="how">
    <div class="section-label">Proceso</div>
    <h2 class="section-title">Tres pasos. Un diagnostico.</h2>
    <div class="steps">
      <div class="step">
        <div class="step-number">01</div>
        <div class="step-icon">📸</div>
        <h3>Fotografia</h3>
        <p>Sacale una foto a la planta afectada. El agente usa vision artificial para identificar signos de enfermedad — lesiones, moho, manchas, patrones de marchitez.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="step">
        <div class="step-number">02</div>
        <div class="step-icon">🔬</div>
        <h3>Diagnostico</h3>
        <p>El modelo identifica el patogeno mas probable y lo cruza con nuestra base de datos curada de peptidos antimicrobianos con eficacia comprobada.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="step">
        <div class="step-number">03</div>
        <div class="step-icon">🧬</div>
        <h3>Recomendacion</h3>
        <p>Recibis una recomendacion personalizada: peptido especifico, concentracion, metodo de aplicacion y referencias cientificas.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <footer>
    <p>Zea — Hackathon Aleph 2026</p>
  </footer>
</Layout>

<style>
  nav {
    position: fixed;
    top: 0;
    left: 0;
    right: 0;
    z-index: 100;
    padding: 16px 32px;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: space-between;
    background: rgba(10, 15, 10, 0.85);
    backdrop-filter: blur(20px);
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
  }

  .logo {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 10px;
    font-weight: 700;
    font-size: 18px;
    letter-spacing: -0.3px;
  }

  .logo-icon {
    width: 32px;
    height: 32px;
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--green), var(--green-dim));
    border-radius: 8px;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    font-size: 18px;
  }

  .nav-links {
    display: flex;
    gap: 32px;
    list-style: none;
  }

  .nav-links a {
    color: var(--text-dim);
    text-decoration: none;
    font-size: 14px;
    font-weight: 500;
    transition: color 0.2s;
  }

  .nav-links a:hover { color: var(--green); }

  .nav-cta {
    background: var(--green);
    color: var(--bg);
    border: none;
    padding: 8px 20px;
    border-radius: 20px;
    font-family: var(--font);
    font-weight: 600;
    font-size: 14px;
    cursor: pointer;
    text-decoration: none;
    transition: transform 0.2s, box-shadow 0.2s;
  }

  .nav-cta:hover {
    transform: translateY(-1px);
    box-shadow: 0 4px 20px var(--green-glow);
  }

  .hero {
    padding: 140px 32px 80px;
    max-width: 1200px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    text-align: center;
    position: relative;
  }

  .hero-badge {
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 8px;
    padding: 6px 16px;
    background: var(--bg-elevated);
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    border-radius: 20px;
    font-size: 13px;
    color: var(--text-dim);
    margin-bottom: 32px;
  }

  .hero-badge .dot {
    width: 6px;
    height: 6px;
    background: var(--green);
    border-radius: 50%;
    animation: pulse 2s ease-in-out infinite;
  }

  @keyframes pulse {
    0%, 100% { opacity: 1; }
    50% { opacity: 0.4; }
  }

  h1 {
    font-size: clamp(40px, 7vw, 72px);
    font-weight: 700;
    line-height: 1.05;
    letter-spacing: -2px;
    margin-bottom: 24px;
  }

  h1 .highlight {
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--green), #86efac);
    -webkit-background-clip: text;
    -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
    background-clip: text;
  }

  .hero-sub {
    font-size: 18px;
    color: var(--text-dim);
    max-width: 600px;
    margin: 0 auto 48px;
    line-height: 1.6;
  }

  .hero-actions {
    display: flex;
    gap: 16px;
    justify-content: center;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
  }

  .btn-primary {
    background: var(--green);
    color: var(--bg);
    border: none;
    padding: 14px 32px;
    border-radius: 28px;
    font-family: var(--font);
    font-weight: 600;
    font-size: 16px;
    cursor: pointer;
    text-decoration: none;
    transition: all 0.2s;
  }

  .btn-primary:hover {
    transform: translateY(-2px);
    box-shadow: 0 8px 30px var(--green-glow);
  }

  .btn-secondary {
    background: transparent;
    color: var(--text);
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    padding: 14px 32px;
    border-radius: 28px;
    font-family: var(--font);
    font-weight: 500;
    font-size: 16px;
    cursor: pointer;
    transition: all 0.2s;
  }

  .btn-secondary:hover {
    border-color: var(--border-active);
    background: var(--bg-elevated);
  }

  .stats {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(4, 1fr);
    gap: 1px;
    background: var(--border);
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    border-radius: var(--radius);
    overflow: hidden;
    max-width: 900px;
    margin: 80px auto 0;
  }

  .stat {
    background: var(--bg-elevated);
    padding: 32px 24px;
    text-align: center;
  }

  .stat-value {
    font-size: 28px;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--green);
    font-family: var(--mono);
  }

  .stat-label {
    font-size: 13px;
    color: var(--text-muted);
    margin-top: 6px;
  }

  .section {
    padding: 100px 32px;
    max-width: 1200px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  .section-label {
    font-size: 13px;
    font-weight: 600;
    color: var(--green);
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 2px;
    margin-bottom: 16px;
  }

  .section-title {
    font-size: clamp(28px, 4vw, 42px);
    font-weight: 700;
    letter-spacing: -1px;
    margin-bottom: 60px;
  }

  .steps {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
    gap: 24px;
  }

  .step {
    background: var(--bg-elevated);
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    border-radius: var(--radius);
    padding: 36px 28px;
    transition: border-color 0.3s, transform 0.3s;
  }

  .step:hover {
    border-color: var(--border-active);
    transform: translateY(-4px);
  }

  .step-number {
    font-family: var(--mono);
    font-size: 13px;
    color: var(--green);
    margin-bottom: 16px;
  }

  .step-icon {
    font-size: 36px;
    margin-bottom: 16px;
  }

  .step h3 {
    font-size: 20px;
    font-weight: 600;
    margin-bottom: 10px;
  }

  .step p {
    font-size: 14px;
    color: var(--text-dim);
    line-height: 1.6;
  }

  footer {
    padding: 40px 32px;
    border-top: 1px solid var(--border);
    text-align: center;
    color: var(--text-muted);
    font-size: 13px;
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .stats { grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr); }
    .steps { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
    .nav-links { display: none; }
  }
</style>
